 Two important parameters are the azimuth angle and the elevation angle
 (or tilt) of the antenna.
 The antenna azimuth (shown in Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:Antenna-azimuth"

\end_inset

