 The goal of the optimization is to increase network capacity.
 The implementation involves a deterministic fitness selection scheme, a
 problem specific recombination operator and an improved mutation operator.
 After the initial identification of the best individuals, a local optimization
 technique is used to improve their fitness.
\end_layout

