 The objective function for coverage optimization may be defined as follows:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{\mathrm{cov}}=\frac{A_{\mathrm{covered}}}{A_{\mathrm{total}}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

